Preview CBSA/CSA FIPS Codes

Source: R/parse_geo_main.R
geo_preview.Rd

geo_preview() previews cbsa metadata for use in filtering of core data sets. It also saves the outputs with an invisible return.

Usage

geo_preview(geo, within = NULL, type = NULL)

Arguments

geo

Character vector. Vector of columns to preview/return from CBSA data

within

character vector. Vector of state abbreviations to filter data with.

type

character scalar. Scalar variable indicating type of data to return. Acceptable values are "metro" and "micro".

Value

printout of data or data.frame of filtered cbsa data.frame

Examples


geo_preview( geo="cbsa", within="LA" )
#>
